}
  XFSIO.SYS n..|OFF

This resident command provides fast
SIO support for the XF551 disk drive.
You must specify the drive numbers
(1-4,8) of the XF551 units to be
accelerated.

Data transfer runs about 2.5 times
faster than the standard SIO rate, but
the speed gain is only noticeable if
the disk was formatted in fast mode.
See the FORMAT command.

During fast SIO operations, the
keyboard is disabled to avoid
interference.
